Rating: 4
We really enjoyed this dish. There is a restaurant in town that serves an "Indian Spiced Chicken" and this is amazingly close. Few little changes I made were: chicken for myself (I can not have turkey) and apple cider vinegar instead of red wine. My husband devoured 2 turkey cutlets, and I wish I had made more than one chicken breast for left overs! Served it with sprouted quinoa and English peas that I also seasoned with coriander and cinnamon. Delish!

